{"tid":1582450,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［黑警陰謀論］樓下保安崗懐疑坐住隻狗","createTime":"2019-09-20T05:13:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T06:41:03.000Z","uid":321421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e607eb0cb59af9e30f1dfced4556c5e57314177f","tid":1582450,"uid":321421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T05:13:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">是咁的，小妹啱啱出門口發現樓下個白衫保安行開咗，保安崗坐住個藍色恤衫嘅男人。</span><br />\n<br />\n前日夜晚翻屋企，有六個藍衫警上咗頂樓，我覺得好奇怪，即刻打開電視睇電梯cctv，平時都睇到，<span style=\"color: red;\">嗰晚突然無咗個台</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n琴晚翻屋企上到自己嗰層一開電梯門見到個綠色軍裝喺我屋企條巷仔行出嚟，有<span style=\"color: red;\">盾牌有頭盔有棍</span><br />\n<br />\n啱啱出門口翻學見到有隻疑似狗坐咗喺保安崗，佢同我對望咗好多下，平時啲保安都係起碼五字頭，呢個目測<span style=\"color: red;\">二三十大大隻</span><br />\n<br />\n我依家好驚，有冇手足同樣情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">利申，住黃大仙舊式公屋</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ace03929bba32cbc184e3e94fe4c103fffe68143","tid":1582450,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T05:14:30.000Z","msg":"[公海 文宣整合] 9.29全球反極權集會 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1581746\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1581746</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">9.29 Global Anti Totalitarianism 文宣、資訊、行動整合Channel</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/AntiChinazi929\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FAntiChinazi929&d=56TVgGSmQeZ0yTrvrOoz8vQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=4fafd180\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/AntiChinazi929</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>9.29 Global Anti Totalitarianism 公海</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ&d=56TVgGSmQeZ0yTrvrOoz8vQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=7a7b9ce6\" target=\"